snippet.title: New Mario Maker Fan Game! // Custom Mario Maker - Build and Share Mario Levels on PC!
snippet.description:
Custom Mario Maker is an AMAZING new Mario Maker fan game that has lots of new items, new enemies, and new power ups to use. This is similar to other Mario Maker fan games like Super Mario Construct, Mario Multiverse, Mario Editor, Super Mario Maker World Engine, Super Mario Bros X, Super Mario Unimaker, and more! You can build your own levels and share them with the world! You can find the download to this and find levels to play in the OFFICIAL Custom Mario Maker Discord server linked below.
📺 SUBSCRIBE: https://www.youtube.com/c/BrickGameStudios?sub_confirmation=1
👋 MY DISCORD: https://dsc.gg/brickgame
⛳ MY TWITCH: https://www.twitch.tv/brickgamestudios
➡️Custom SMM Discord: https://discord.gg/PBwYZeRyDM
➡️Custom SMM Developer: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC0V0lkLLePltNv_OfmBRWnA
#brickgamestudios #custommariomaker #fangame

Thank you for watching my videos, it means the world to me ❤️
